  "root_text": {
    "an7.3:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7.3 ",
    "an7.3:0.2": "1. Dhanavagga ",
    "an7.3:0.3": "Saṅkhittabalasutta ",
    "an7.3:1.1": "Evaṁ me sutaṁ—",
    "an7.3:1.2": "ekaṁ samayaṁ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṁ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme …pe… ",
    "an7.3:1.3": "sattimāni, bhikkhave, balāni. ",
    "an7.3:1.4": "Katamāni satta? ",
    "an7.3:1.5": "Saddhābalaṁ, vīriyabalaṁ, hirībalaṁ, ottappabalaṁ, satibalaṁ, samādhibalaṁ, paññābalaṁ. ",
    "an7.3:1.6": "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, satta balānīti. ",
    "an7.3:2.1": "Saddhābalaṁ vīriyañca, ",
    "an7.3:2.2": "hirī ottappiyaṁ balaṁ; ",
    "an7.3:2.3": "Satibalaṁ samādhi ca, ",
    "an7.3:2.4": "paññā ve sattamaṁ balaṁ; ",
    "an7.3:2.5": "Etehi balavā bhikkhu, ",
    "an7.3:2.6": "sukhaṁ jīvati paṇḍito. ",
    "an7.3:3.1": "Yoniso vicine dhammaṁ, ",
    "an7.3:3.2": "paññāyatthaṁ vipassati; ",
    "an7.3:3.3": "Pajjotasseva nibbānaṁ, ",
    "an7.3:3.4": "vimokkho hoti cetaso”ti. ",
    "an7.3:3.5": "Tatiyaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an7.3:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 7.3 ",
    "an7.3:0.2": "1. Wealth ",
    "an7.3:0.3": "Powers in Brief ",
    "an7.3:1.1": "So I have heard. ",
    "an7.3:1.2": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. … ",
    "an7.3:1.3": "“Mendicants, there are these seven powers. ",
    "an7.3:1.4": "What seven? ",
    "an7.3:1.5": "The powers of faith, energy, conscience, prudence, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. ",
    "an7.3:1.6": "These are the seven powers. ",
    "an7.3:2.1": "The powers are faith and energy, ",
    "an7.3:2.2": "conscience and prudence, ",
    "an7.3:2.3": "mindfulness and immersion, ",
    "an7.3:2.4": "and wisdom as the seventh power. ",
    "an7.3:2.5": "Empowered by these, ",
    "an7.3:2.6": "an astute mendicant lives happily. ",
    "an7.3:3.1": "They should examine the teaching rationally, ",
    "an7.3:3.2": "discerning the meaning with wisdom. ",
    "an7.3:3.3": "The liberation of their heart ",
    "an7.3:3.4": "is like a lamp going out.” "
  },
  "variant_text": {
